Class FlexTableBulkRenderer

java.lang.Object
  com.google.gwt.widgetideas.table.client.TableBulkRenderer
      com.google.gwt.widgetideas.table.client.FlexTableBulkRenderer

public class FlexTableBulkRenderer
extends TableBulkRenderer

A helper class to enable bulk loading of FlexTable. Once we have 1.5 support it will extend TableBulkLoader.

Important note: Must use FlexTable in overrides package NOT the standard 1.4 FlexTable.
